Freepik.types: All types of files allowed (except videos)

AdobeStock Video.link:
https://stock.adobe.com/video/{title}/{image-ID}

Make sure to exclude any additional information after the image ID and avoid including country codes or variations. The link should end immediately after the image ID. 🚫🌍

Incorrect Example: ❌
https://stock.adobe.com/in/video/beautiful-tender-girl/601584439

Correct Example: ✅
https://stock.adobe.com/video/beautiful-tender-girl/601584439

Please note that our bot will only process your request if the link is in the correct format. ✨
